history.content:
CS 88 (http://cs88-website.github.io/) is an intro CS course for the new Data Science major! We cover many of the same topics as CS 61A, with an emphasis on data analysis. We are looking to hire academic interns / lab assistants for the fall semester. This is a great opportunity to get involved with the data science initiative and help scale a class that has grown to over 200 students!

Please submit your application before 8/19: https://goo.gl/forms/ffNXjLzD01xyNlGR2

Feel free to email me if you have any questions: andrewtan@berkeley.edu
history.subject: CS 88 Academic Interns / Lab Assistants
